ReviewContent: Emma is an incredible sound healer, I could not recommend this experience enough. She took the time before we got started to check-in with each of us over tea, creating the space for a real transformational and relaxation. I loved it so much, that I already have my next sound healing scheduled. I cant thank Emma enough for this sweet and special offering. She has a true gift and Im so grateful that she shares it with us!

I have experienced her sound baths in many different settings - yoga studios, private homes, retreats - and it s always a unique and healing experience. Thank you, Emma, for sharing your gift!
